### 廊坊社保管理系统 - API测试脚本
### 使用方法：在VS Code中安装REST Client插件，点击"Send Request"即可测试

### 变量定义
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### ==================== 登录 ====================

### 1. 登录获取token
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "jingbanren",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### ==================== 人员信息管理 ====================

### 2. 查询人员登记列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/shebao/person/registration/list?pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. 新增人员登记
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/person/registration
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试人员",
  "idCardNo": "130102199001011234",
  "gender": "1",
  "birthDate": "1990-01-01",
  "streetOfficeId": 1,
  "villageCommitteeId": 1,
  "contactPhone": "13800138000",
  "householdAddress": "河北省廊坊市某街道某村",
  "subsidyType": "land_loss_resident",
  "remark": "测试数据"
}

### 4. 查询人员详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/shebao/person/registration/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 提交审核
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/person/registration/submit/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "remark": "请审核"
}

### 6. 查询待复核列表（复核人）
GET {{baseUrl}}/shebao/person/review/list?pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. 复核通过
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/person/review/1/pass
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "remark": "复核通过"
}

### 8. 复核驳回
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/person/review/1/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "remark": "身份证号格式错误，请修改"
}

### ==================== 待遇核定管理 ====================

### 9. 生成预到龄通知
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/benefit/notice/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "noticeMonth": "2026-04",
  "ageThreshold": 60
}

### 10. 查询预到龄通知列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/shebao/benefit/notice/list?pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. 单个待遇核定
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/benefit/determination
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "personId": 1,
  "subsidyType": "land_loss_resident",
  "monthlyAmount": 500.00,
  "startMonth": "2026-01",
  "bankName": "中国工商银行",
  "bankAccountNo": "6222021234567890123",
  "bankAccountName": "测试人员",
  "remark": "待遇核定"
}

### 12. 批量待遇核定（Excel导入）
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/benefit/determination/batch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="benefit_batch.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< ./benefit_batch.xlsx
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### 13. 查询待遇核定列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/shebao/benefit/determination/list?pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================== 待遇管理 ====================

### 14. 修改发放信息
PUT {{baseUrl}}/shebao/benefit/modify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "personId": 1,
  "subsidyType": "land_loss_resident",
  "monthlyAmount": 550.00,
  "bankName": "中国农业银行",
  "bankAccountNo": "6228451234567890123",
  "reason": "更换银行卡"
}

### 15. 待遇暂停
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/benefit/suspension
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "personId": 1,
  "subsidyType": "land_loss_resident",
  "suspensionReason": "death",
  "suspensionDate": "2026-01-15",
  "remark": "人员死亡，暂停发放"
}

### 16. 待遇恢复
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/benefit/suspension/resume
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "personId": 1,
  "subsidyType": "land_loss_resident",
  "resumeDate": "2026-02-01",
  "remark": "已认证，恢复发放"
}

### 17. 待遇认证
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/benefit/certification
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "personId": 1,
  "subsidyType": "land_loss_resident",
  "certificationType": "april",
  "certificationDate": "2026-04-15",
  "remark": "4月认证"
}

### ==================== 支付结算 ====================

### 18. 生成支付计划
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/payment/plan/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subsidyType": "land_loss_resident",
  "startMonth": "2026-01",
  "endMonth": "2026-12",
  "streetOfficeId": 1,
  "villageCommitteeId": 1
}

### 19. 查询支付计划列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/shebao/payment/plan/list?pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 20. 创建发放批次
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/payment/batch/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subsidyType": "land_loss_resident",
  "paymentMonth": "2026-01",
  "planIds": [1, 2, 3]
}

### 21. 批次复核（复核人）
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/payment/batch/1/review
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approved": true,
  "remark": "复核通过"
}

### 22. 批次审批（审批人）
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/payment/batch/1/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approved": true,
  "remark": "审批通过"
}

### 23. 上传财务系统（审批人）
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/payment/batch/1/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "remark": "已上传财务系统"
}

### ==================== 财务管理 ====================

### 24. 查询批次列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/shebao/finance/batch/list?pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 25. 查询批次详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/shebao/finance/batch/detail/202601150001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 26. 生成银行文件
GET {{baseUrl}}/shebao/finance/bank/file/202601150001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 27. 提交银行发放
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/finance/bank/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "batchNo": "202601150001",
  "remark": "已提交银行"
}

### 28. 导入发放结果
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/finance/bank/import
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="payment_result.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< ./payment_result.xlsx
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="batchNo"

202601150001
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### 29. 失败处理 - 信息更正
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/finance/failure/handle
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "distributionId": 1,
  "handleType": "correct",
  "correctedBankAccountNo": "6228451234567890123",
  "remark": "银行卡号更正"
}

### 30. 失败处理 - 二次发放
POST {{baseUrl}}/shebao/finance/failure/handle
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "distributionId": 1,
  "handleType": "retry",
  "remark": "二次发放"
}

### 31. 查询财务账户列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/shebao/finance/account/list
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================== 审计报表 ====================

### 32. 查询审批记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/shebao/audit/approval/list?pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 33. 查询发放明细
GET {{baseUrl}}/shebao/audit/detail/list?pageNum=1&pageSize=10&startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 34. 统计汇总
GET {{baseUrl}}/shebao/audit/statistics?subsidyType=land_loss_resident&year=2026
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================== 审批历史 ====================

### 35. 查询业务审批历史
GET {{baseUrl}}/shebao/approval/history/person_registration/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
